{
  "stem": "9601.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If you kill a Jew, you know, you'll be OK.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think it's not that-- you know, killing is not that simple when you live in a little village and you know people face-to-face.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to have the intellectuals approve it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the intellectual-- the intellectuals, their parents-- their father and mother, their uncles, their aunts, or maybe even their grandfathers-- and when it came to do this thing-- Because our village was ready.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, they organized horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said-- you, you, you to their neighbors.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You' bring your horse and wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Today we're going to take the Jews to the ghetto-- to Rovne.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the men were called up during the night [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to come into a certain place-- the most popular place there, which was like a-- like a motel, a early version.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't actually, but it was an inn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had, you know, nice facilities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They had basements and cellars and ice, and-- because you have to provide all those services.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's when it all started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was the beginning of all the destruction of our village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not by strangers, by natives-- people that you knew every day, people that you saw every day except when they-- when they were away to college.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the Germans came in and they came home, that's when things became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By that--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
